complaint_details: Television worked well for only 3 weeks after purchase date. There were intense sparks and after that television stopped working.
MS office is not accepting the correct product key. Please resolve it asap.

Inspite of pre-booking couple days before, the staff asked for the payment details citing that their online record do not shows our registration. Order Number: 897456246844 which was delivered on 10th Jan 2023.
The product stopped working after the technician replaced the coolant.
It has been 2 months since the RO purifier servicing is due but there is no support provided from Vendor.
